Different document shapes are
supported:

+-----+  +-----+  +-----+  +-----+
|     |  |{d}  |  |{s}  |  |{io} |
|     |  |     |  |     |  |     |
|     |  |     |  |     |  |     |
+-----+  +-----+  +-----+  +-----+

But these shapes only really apply to
rectangles:

+-----+  +-----+  +-----+  +-----+
|     |  |{d}  |  |{s}  |  |{io} |
|  +--+  |  +--+  |  +--+  |  +--+
|  |     |  |     |  |     |  |
+--+     +--+     +--+     +--+
